      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You're struggling to come to terms with the fact that your entire existence was built on a flawed foundation, and now that's been exposed. It's as if you've been living in a dream world, and the wake-up call is painful and disorienting. The loss of your identity, reputation, and sense of self can be a crushing blow, making it difficult to envision a way forward.",
